OL,6,FHowever, there are calls for more
OL,7,Fprovision with La Passerelle and Mont
OL,8,Fa Labbe nearing or at capacity.
OL,10,FThe figures of children and young
OL,11,Fpeople diagnosed with autism and
OL,12,Frecorded by CAMHS over the past four
OL,13,Fyears:
OL,15,FCharlie was diagnosed with autism at
OL,16,F13 and attended one of Jersey's
OL,17,Fspecialist schools. He believes more
OL,18,Fschools would help other autistic
OL,19,Fpeople.
