OL,6,FHe explains: "If it's in places closer
OL,7,Fto them and more places (it would)
OL,8,Fhelp neurodivergent people feel
OL,9,Fcomfortable.
OL,11,F"It's important, not just for me, but
OL,12,Ffor autistic people in general to have
OL,13,Fa place where they're able to have an
OL,14,Feducation as well, just like everyone
OL,15,Felse in a way that they feel safe and
OL,16,Fcomfortable in."
OL,18,FTeacher Sarah believes the model at Le
OL,19,FPasserelle could be replicated.
