OL,6,FShe says: "If we could share what we
OL,7,Fare doing within our school with our
OL,8,Fmainstream colleagues that can only
OL,9,Fsupport and firm their vision and
OL,10,Fvalues for inclusion and what they're
OL,11,Foffering neurodiverse children in
OL,12,Fmainstream schools.
OL,14,F"It's about reaching out now and
OL,15,Fsaying look what we can do to support
OL,16,Fyou."
OL,18,FITV Channel spoke to Education
OL,19,FMinister Deputy Rob Ward, who said it
OL,20,Fis a complex issue but there is more
OL,21,Funderstanding of the condition.
